      "content": "thanks. the pattern is weird though. it's mostly small, high-value components like microchips and sensors. they just seem to vanish from the middle of the racks during the night shift. i can't find any broken seals or signs of forced entry, it's like they just disappeared into thin air. any idea why that would happen?",
